OL,3,CPrime Minister pledges 'major funding
OL,4,Ccommitment' for future Welsh rail
OL,5,Cschemes
OL,7,FThe Prime Minister is set to back a
OL,8,Fnumber of new rail projects across
OL,9,FWales and pledge a "long term
OL,10,Fcommitment" to future schemes.
OL,12,FOn a visit to South Wales, Sir Keir
OL,13,FStarmer will announce UK Government
OL,14,Fsupport for the privately-funded
OL,15,FCardiff Parkway project to the east of
OL,16,FCardiff, along with a new station at
OL,17,FDeeside Industrial Park.
OL,19,FIt comes as Transport for Wales sets
OL,20,Fout a pipeline of rail improvements
OL,21,Festimated at upto #14bn.
