OL,3,CPrime Minister pledges 'major funding
OL,4,Ccommitment' for future Welsh rail
OL,5,Cschemes
OL,7,FThe Prime Minister says his government
OL,8,Fis committed to "investment for the
OL,9,Flong term", although little further
OL,10,Ffunding beyond the #440m set out in
OL,11,Fthe 2025 Spending Review has been
OL,12,Fconfirmed.
OL,14,F"This Government is turning the page
OL,15,Fon historic dither and delay with
OL,16,Fseven new stations, thousands of jobs,
OL,17,Fand a generational commitment to build
OL,18,Fa rail network fit for Wales' future"
OL,19,Fhe said.
