OL,7,F"We warmly welcome the UK Government's
OL,8,Fsupport for these plans and for their
OL,9,Fcommitment to putting right the
OL,10,Finjustice of Welsh rail underfunding
OL,11,Fleft by the previous government" said
OL,12,FFirst Minister Eluned Morgan
OL,14,F"We are now in an unprecedented
OL,15,Fposition to deliver the next chapter
OL,16,Fof transformation for rail services in
OL,17,FWales," she added.
