OL,7,FIt's intended to boost public
OL,8,Ftransport and economic development in
OL,9,Fan area to the east of Cardiff poorly
OL,10,Fserved by buses and trains, with the
OL,11,FUK Government claiming it could serve
OL,12,F800,000 passengers per year.
OL,14,FAlthough planning permission was
OL,15,Fgranted by Cardiff Council in 2022,
OL,16,Fthe project was called in by the Welsh
OL,17,FGovernment later that year.
OL,19,FIt was eventually approved by First
OL,20,FMinister Eluned Morgan in January 2025.
