OL,7,FThese could include:
OL,9,FThe level of investment in rail
OL,10,Fprojects in Wales has increasingly
OL,11,Fbecome the subject of intense debate.
OL,13,FThe Welsh Government doesn't have
OL,14,Fcontrol of rail infrastructure in
OL,15,FWales, with the exception of the Core
OL,16,FValley Lines that form the majority of
OL,17,Fthe South Wales Metro.
