OL,3,CPrime Minister pledges 'major funding
OL,4,Ccommitment' for future Welsh rail
OL,5,Cschemes
OL,7,F"After more than #1bn has already been
OL,8,Fspent on the South Wales Metro, it is
OL,9,Fdisappointing that there is still no
OL,10,Fcommitment to follow through with UK
OL,11,FConservative Government plans to
OL,12,Felectrify the North Wales Main Line, a
OL,13,Fproject that businesses and
OL,14,Fcommunities have long called for" said
OL,15,FShadow Cabinet Secretary for Transport
OL,16,F& Infrastructure, Sam Rowlands MS.
OL,18,FThe Liberal Democrats accuse the UK
OL,19,FGovernment of "desperately reheating
OL,20,Fold announcements".
